snippet.title: Episode 222 – Amber Heard vs Johnny Depp
snippet.description:
On this episode:
Amber Heard gaslighting and hitting Captain Jack Sparrow • Dating a fork thrower • Table 19 and other Anna Kendrick movie recommendations • UFC 247 • The Raps current win streak • Rebel Wilson
Yasin & Syed are the hosts of the weekly Crash & Flow podcast. They talk about stand-up comedy, movies, TV shows, animals, relationships, travel, life, MMA, and whatever rabbit hole they recently fell into. Special guests often stop by the Toronto studio to chat as well.
